This report compares what QuickBooks is billing each customer against the monthly billing amount and product subscription recorded in ClickUp. It is the strongest starting POC because both data sources are already syncing daily into BigQuery — no new schema mapping or CovrDB integration is required. Discrepancies surface either overcharges (CS relationship risk) or undercharges (revenue leakage), making the output immediately actionable for both CS and Finance.

