Given the scale of Covr's BI needs (4 departments, ad-hoc analysis, natural language queries), **Looker (Google Cloud core) Standard** is the most appropriate option. The per-user costs scale with adoption — departments can begin with Viewer licenses and upgrade analysts/rep leads to Standard as needed. The free tier (Looker Studio) is insufficient due to the lack of a semantic layer and Explore capabilities.

